intent.user_query: What is the percentage of service tickets resolved within one week?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets WHERE ResolutionDate IS NOT NULL AND ResolutionDate - TicketDate <= 7) / CAST(COUNT(*) AS DECIMAL(10,2)) * 100 FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets;

arguments.sql: SELECT (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets WHERE ResolutionDate IS NOT NULL AND ResolutionDate - TicketDate <= 7) / CAST(COUNT(*) AS DECIMAL(10,2)) * 100 FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
